---
---

<section id="about" class="py-24 lg:py-32 bg-landrover-limestone">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
    
    <!-- Intro -->
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-20">
      <p class="text-landrover-coniston text-xs tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-4">Our Philosophy</p>
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-landrover-santorini mb-8 leading-tight">
        Land is not just acquired — <br class="hidden md:block" />it is felt.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-landrover-marine/80 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        Every property carries a rhythm, a memory of wind, light, and time. 
        We listen before we build, observe before we propose, honoring the natural 
        intelligence of each place.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Three Pillars -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 lg:gap-16">
      
      <!-- Philosophy -->
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-6 flex items-center justify-center border border-landrover-coniston/30 rounded-full">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-landrover-coniston" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl text-landrover-santorini mb-4">Philosophy</h3>
        <p class="text-landrover-marine/70 leading-relaxed">
          Our philosophy is rooted in balance: between architecture and landscape, 
          investment and emotion, vision and authenticity.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Experience -->
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-6 flex items-center justify-center border border-landrover-coniston/30 rounded-full">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-landrover-coniston" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl text-landrover-santorini mb-4">Experience</h3>
        <p class="text-landrover-marine/70 leading-relaxed">
          Shaped by years of deep immersion in the Costa Rican market. 
          Our experience is measured in relationships built with trust and continuity.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Innovation -->
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-6 flex items-center justify-center border border-landrover-coniston/30 rounded-full">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-landrover-coniston" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl text-landrover-santorini mb-4">Innovation</h3>
        <p class="text-landrover-marine/70 leading-relaxed">
          We merge local knowledge with global perspective, 
          always one step ahead, yet deeply grounded in place.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Legacy Statement -->
    <div class="mt-24 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="relative border-l-2 border-accent-sand">
        <blockquote class="pl-8 text-xl md:text-2xl text-landrover-marine font-serif italic leading-relaxed">
          "This is a place curated by a family, shaped by decades of hosting, feeding, 
          and caring for people in Nosara through La Luna, Coyol, and Esh."
        </blockquote>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
